			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Player makes a comment after picking up Dargger of Paralysing.&#xD;&#xA;The specific AD depends on whether we know that Father Lorgan was killed with a dagger or not.&#xD;&#xA;This AD only happens if you know that Father Lorgan was killed." />
